NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::PkgVersionIfModuleWithPod - Apply PkgVersion to .pm
    files with =pod sections

VERSION
    version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
    In your Dist::Zilla `dist.ini':

        [PkgVersionIfModuleWithPod]

DESCRIPTION
    Like Dist::Zilla::Plugin::PkgVersion, but only for .pm files with =pod
    sections.

